HEADWORD: Instate
<hw>In*state"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Instated</conjf>; <pos>p. pr. & vb. n.</pos>
<conjf>Instating</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To set, place, or establish, as
